{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762173662984","path":null,"data":{"id":4306,"title":"ManuLife:「宏摯傳承」產品更新及相關事宜","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1753265366460,"tags":["宏利保險","宏利澳門"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ManuLife就以下事宜作出更新調整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"color: #09b04d;\">一、產品更新「宏摯傳承保障計劃」</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 於<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">2025年7月21日</span></strong></span>，就熱賣儲蓄保險計劃<strong>「宏摯傳承保障計劃」</strong>作出更新。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 產品更新後，「宏摯傳承保障計劃」設有合共<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">7種</span>保單貨幣</strong>，並同時推出<strong>全新<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">2年保費繳付期保單</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 計劃亦同時<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">上調3年保費繳付期</span>保單的回報</strong>。新生意的3年保費繳付期保單下的保證現金價值及非保證終期紅利已由<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>2025年7月21日</strong></span></span>起向上調整。</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-07-23/mceclip2_f4c19367ba874671853b79485d20ca82.png\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #09b04d;\">二、新里程保費回贈優惠</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 新里程保費回贈優惠廣適用於<strong>「宏摯傳承保障計劃」之兒童受保人保單</strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 由<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">2025年7月21日至10月20日</span></strong></span>申請<strong>「宏摯傳承保障計劃」</strong>，如受保人的年齡在保單簽發時為<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">18歲或以下</span></strong>，保單持有人可享一次性可高達基本計劃<strong>合資格保費的<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">30%的保費回贈</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"color: #09b04d;\">三、盈傳創富保障計劃3「升級」優惠</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 由<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>2025年7月21日至10月20日</strong></span></span>內申請<strong>盈傳創富保障計劃3</strong>保單並符合以下資格條件，可享以下「升級」優惠。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>申請資格:</strong></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-07-23/mceclip4_2672dca9617543c9ad30002bd4b604b3.png\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">申請程序:</span></strong></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-07-23/mceclip6_8a0f09e8be7d4b46bb8145286ddc42f4.png\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #09b04d;\">四、宏健守護危疾入息保障建議書優化</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 由<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>2025年7月21日</strong></span></span>起，<strong>「宏健守護危疾入息保障」</strong>的建議書將會更新如下。</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-07-23/mceclip7_03bade374a714fcf8ab03b053c08e52e.png\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"NewsFlash - 2025 FAE Campaigns_HK_BR_TC.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-07-23/NewsFlash - 2025 FAE Campaigns_HK_BR_TC_b0ddb4f9cf4544b5b006b7baa93b91d6.pdf","uploadTime":1753262426594,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"NewsFlash - 2025 FAE Campaigns_HK_BR_EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-07-23/NewsFlash - 2025 FAE Campaigns_HK_BR_EN_9dfa2dd6741a45f8a6e974ba52f2b74c.pdf","uploadTime":1753262907636,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"MANULIFE","companyName":"宏利保險","productCodes":["MANULIFE:GENESIS","MANULIFE:WIOP3"],"productNames":["宏摯傳承保障計劃","盈傳創富保障計劃3"],"companyCodes":["MANULIFE"],"companyNames":["宏利保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1753090154082,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}